<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="drop-n">drop <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /drɒp/    美 /drɑːp/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>滴；[常用复数] 滴剂：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>drops of</strong> rain
雨滴</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>eye drops</strong>
眼药水</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[常用单数] 微量；少量：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She has not <strong>a drop of</strong> patience. 
她一点耐心也没有。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[常用单数] 下落；下降：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a drop in air pressure
气压下降</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>sharp</strong> / rapid <strong>drop in</strong> profits
利润急剧/快速下降</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>[常用单数] 倾斜或垂直的距离</strong></h4></div>